## Configuration -- Liquibase Properties (Profiles)

Each environment contains:

    Profiles/<ENV>/liquibase.properties

### Example (PostgreSQL)

``` properties
url=jdbc:postgresql://<host>:5432/<db_name>?currentSchema=<schema_name>&sslmode=verify-full
driver=org.postgresql.Driver
username=<db_user>
password=${cyberark.password}

logLevel=debug
outputFile=SQL_OUT/${env}.sql
defaultSchemaName=<schema_name>
```

> Adapt driver and URL format for other databases if required.

