## Release Changelog (`release.xml`)

### Important ChangeSet Attributes

  Attribute     Meaning                        Recommended Value
  ------------- ------------------------------ -------------------
  runOnChange   Re-executes when SQL changes   true
  runAlways     Executes every run             false
  id            Unique identifier              Required
  labels        Jenkins filtering tag          Optional
  context       Environment selection          Optional
  author        Creator name                   Required

### Example ChangeSet

``` xml
<databaseChangeLog
 xmlns="http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog"
 xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
 xsi:schemaLocation="
 http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog
 http://www.liquibase.org/xml/ns/dbchangelog/dbchangelog-3.8.xsd">

    <changeSet
        id="001-create-table"
        author="h59281"
        runOnChange="true"
        labels="1.0-release"
        context="release-1.0">

        <sqlFile
            path="Scripts/Project_name/create_table_1.sql"
            relativeToChangelogFile="true"/>

        <rollback>
            <sql>
                DROP TABLE IF EXISTS project_name.my_table;
            </sql>
        </rollback>

    </changeSet>

</databaseChangelog>
```

