## Adding New Change-Sets

1.  Create folder:

```{=html}
<!-- -->
```
    Release_<project_name>/feature_xyz/

2.  Add XML file.
3.  Define change-set with unique id & author.

### Example

``` xml
<changeSet
    id="005-add-index"
    author="idge"
    runOnChange="true"
    labels="2.0-release"
    context="release-2.0">

    <sqlFile
        path="Scripts/add_index.sql"
        relativeToChangelogFile="true"/>

    <rollback>
        <sql>
            DROP INDEX IF EXISTS idx_my_table_col;
        </sql>
    </rollback>

</changeSet>
```

