## Lifecycle of a ChangeSet

  Phase              Liquibase Behavior
  ------------------ ----------------------------------------------------
  First Execution    Runs SQL and inserts record into DATABASECHANGELOG
  Subsequent Runs    Skipped if checksum unchanged
  runOnChange=true   Re-executes when SQL changes
  runAlways=true     Executes every run
  Rollback           `liquibase rollback <tag>`
  Execution Order    Update = ascending, Rollback = descending

