## Common Issues & Troubleshooting

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  Issue                   Cause                   Solution
  ----------------------- ----------------------- -----------------------
  SQL file not found      Wrong relative path     Verify path

  SSL connection errors   Missing certificates    Verify sslmode & cert
                                                  files

  Missing credential      CyberArk mapping absent Add credential mapping

  Rollback not executed   No rollback block       Add `<rollback>`

  Empty SQL output        No changes detected     Verify
                                                  runOnChange/runAlways
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------

